<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>나뮤니티</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app/nammunity.css">
</head>

<body>

<div id="wrap" class="popup-window">
    <h1>세부 목록</h1>
    {{#detail}}
    <div class="top-area">
        <table>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th>신고 분류:</th>
                    <td>{{type}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>신고 내용:</th>
                    <td>
                        <p class="title">{{#postsListDto}}{{title}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}{{content}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}{{nickname}}{{/usersListDto}}</p>
                        <p class="author">{{#postsListDto}}{{author}}, {{modifiedDate}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}{{author}}, {{modifiedDate}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}{{createdDate}}{{/usersListDto}}</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <span>누적 신고 횟수: {{reportDetails.totalElements}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-area">
        <table>
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th class="no">번호</th>
                <th class="reporter">신고자</th>
                <th class="date">신고일</th>
                <th class="reason">사유</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            {{#reportDetails}}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{id}}</td>
                    <td>{{reporter}}</td>
                    <td>{{reportedDate}}</td>
                    <td class="reason">{{reason}}</td>
                </tr>
            {{/reportDetails}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {{#pages}}
            <div>
                {{#hasPrevious}}
                    첫 페이지: <a href="/admin/my-page/content-report/details?{{#postsListDto}}postsId={{id}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}commentsId={{commentsId}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}userId={{id}}{{/usersListDto}}&page={{firstPage}}">{{firstPage}}</a> | 이전 페이지: <a href="/admin/my-page/content-report/details?{{#postsListDto}}postsId={{id}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}commentsId={{commentsId}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}userId={{id}}{{/usersListDto}}&page={{previousPage}}">{{previousPage}}</a> |
                {{/hasPrevious}}
                {{#displayPages}}
                    {{#isCurrentPage}}
                        | 현재 페이지: {{page}}
                    {{/isCurrentPage}}
                    {{^isCurrentPage}}
                        | <a href="/admin/my-page/content-report/details?{{#postsListDto}}postsId={{id}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}commentsId={{commentsId}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}userId={{id}}{{/usersListDto}}&page={{page}}">{{page}}</a>
                    {{/isCurrentPage}}
                {{/displayPages}}
                {{#hasNext}}
                    | | 다음 페이지: <a href="/admin/my-page/content-report/details?{{#postsListDto}}postsId={{id}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}commentsId={{commentsId}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}userId={{id}}{{/usersListDto}}&page={{nextPage}}">{{nextPage}}</a> | 마지막 페이지: <a href="/admin/my-page/content-report/details?{{#postsListDto}}postsId={{id}}{{/postsListDto}}{{#commentsListDto}}commentsId={{commentsId}}{{/commentsListDto}}{{#usersListDto}}userId={{id}}{{/usersListDto}}&page={{lastPage}}">{{lastPage}}</a>
                {{/hasNext}}
            </div>
        {{/pages}}
    </div>
    {{/detail}}
</div>

{{#exception}}
    <script>
            alert('{{exception}}');
            window.location.href = '{{#signOut}}{{signOut}}{{/signOut}}{{^signOut}}/{{/signOut}}';
        </script>
{{/exception}}
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b/U6ypiBEHpOf/4+1nzFpr53nxSS+GLCkfwBdFNTxtclqqenISfwAzpKaMNFNmj4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
